Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我把作文发回给大家\N{\fnArial\fs16}Now, as I'm handing back your essays,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可能会对...\N{\fnArial\fs16}you may have strong feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,差异悬殊又让人沮丧的评分标准产生强烈不满\N{\fnArial\fs16}about the competitive and discouraging aspects of grading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我很重视大家的意见\N{\fnArial\fs16}I care about what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谁先说?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Who would like to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,F+和D-是一样的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Is an F+ the same as a D-?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕是从来没听过什么F+ Jordan\N{\fnArial\fs16}I don't believe I've ever heard of an F+, Jordan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不过我们可以稍作讨论 - 她就说\N{\fnArial\fs16}- but we can talk about it. - So she said, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"我买了你说的乳白色紧身裤"\N{\fnArial\fs16}"I got those eggshell leggings like you told me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我应她 "乳白色? 我都说了是深紫色啦"\N{\fnArial\fs16}and I said, "Eggshell? I told you eggplant!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,搞笑的吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn? 你有话要说么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn? Was there something you wanted to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有拿到作文\N{\fnArial\fs16}Um, I didn't get my essay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.78,0:01:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是没发给你 Quinn 恐怕下课后你得留下来\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's true, Quinn. I'm afraid I need to see you after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在镜子前给你留个位置哒\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'll save you a place at the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 我很抱歉 但我们得谈谈你的表现\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn, I'm so sorry, but we need to talk about your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 可我今天有点忙\N{\fnArial\fs16}Okay, but I'm kinda in a rush today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来说回我们的期末任务吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Let's go over our last assignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,《我对文化多样性的看法》\N{\fnArial\fs16}"How I feel about polyculturalism."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你写的是"我相当喜欢全棉制品"\N{\fnArial\fs16}You wrote, "I definitely prefer all-cotton."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是指抄袭的话 我可没有\N{\fnArial\fs16}I didn't copy it, if that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 我相信你 问题是...\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, no, I believe you. The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在不想让你惶恐或心烦\N{\fnArial\fs16}now I don't want to panic or upset you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:01:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请务必带着建设性的目光来看待这事\N{\fnArial\fs16}please, take this in a constructive spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但恐怕你的语言艺术学得不咋地\N{\fnArial\fs16}but I'm afraid you're not doing well in Language Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 明天见\N{\fnArial\fs16}Okay. See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你没理解我的意思\N{\fnArial\fs16}I don't think you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你要在下一篇作文里拿到A\N{\fnArial\fs16}You're going to have to get an A on your next essay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,才能保持及格\N{\fnArial\fs16}to maintain a passing grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说"及格或挂科"的那个及格?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You mean, passing as in "passing or failing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是 可别担心\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yes! But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做的就是痛下保证 尽心尽力 和认真刻苦\N{\fnArial\fs16}All it will take is some commitment, dedication, and hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 别啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到的 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs16}You can do it, Quinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我上高中那会儿呀\N{\fnArial\fs16}You know, when I was in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我卯足干劲只为在体操队谋得一席之位\N{\fnArial\fs16}I wanted more than anything to be on the gymnastic team,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可我就是搞不定高杠\N{\fnArial\fs16}but I just couldn't master the high bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我每天训练...\N{\fnArial\fs16}So I practiced every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,随即考验来临 你成功入队了\N{\fnArial\fs16}And the big tryout came and you made the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 不是\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不过就在那个冬天\N{\fnArial\fs16}But that winter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我学会了如何用牙咬着铅笔写字\N{\fnArial\fs16}I learned how to write while holding a pencil in my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你知道这意味着什么吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn? What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我辛苦工作了半天\N{\fnArial\fs16}I put in another twelve-hour day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,结果回家看到的第一件事是...\N{\fnArial\fs16}and the first thing I see when I get home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake\N{\fnArial\fs16}Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我醒啦 - 孩子们哪去了?\N{\fnArial\fs16}- Ah! I'm up! - Where are the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,刚还在这呢... 我想是吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}They were here before... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我非常不满\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm very upset about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我知道啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 我刚想打电话点播电影呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}See, I was trying to call the number for Movie Phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,结果这女人就莫名其妙地接了...\N{\fnArial\fs16}and out of nowhere this woman comes on the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 你在说什么呀?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Jake, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是电话账单么... 我... 那是什么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's not the phone bill. I... what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是Quinn的老师写的信\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's a letter from Quinn's teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她的英语要挂了 因为她没付出任何努力\N{\fnArial\fs16}She's going to fail English because she's not putting in any effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去楼上找她谈谈\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm going up to go talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,凭什么就不能是我来和孩子们谈?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Why can't I ever be the one to talk to the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 不是说你不能啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Honey, it's not that you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是... 一个严格的家教团队好比一个合唱团嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's just... a strong parenting team is like a singing group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,主唱负责领唱\N{\fnArial\fs16}The lead singer carries the tune,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,伴唱的负责给她合音\N{\fnArial\fs16}and the backup singers support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那伴唱们都要做些什么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}But what do the backup singers do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你在恰当的时刻帮腔\N{\fnArial\fs16}You chime in at just the right moment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就保持沉默 这样一说不是很恰当嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}and then you fade into the background. Doesn't that make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要拿个铃鼓什么的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Do I get a tambourine or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈 我能借...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Mom, can I borrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想去动物收留所\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm just going to go run down to the animal shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看有没志愿者的差事啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}and see about volunteering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说他们刚收留了一群病鸟\N{\fnArial\fs16}I heard they got in a new bunch of sick birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 这是学校寄来的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn, this note came from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,担心啥哟\N{\fnArial\fs16}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做的就是在下一篇作文里拿到A\N{\fnArial\fs16}All I have to do is get, like, an A on my next essay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就没问题啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}and I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对这事我押上拉斯维加斯的赌注赔率\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'll take the Vegas odds on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 我们得鼓舞士气\N{\fnArial\fs16}Daria, we need to be encouraging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下 Quinn 亲爱的 这不仅仅是一篇文章的问题\N{\fnArial\fs16}Sit down, Quinn. Honey, this isn't just about one essay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是要你制定人生目标并实现\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's about setting goals in life and going after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我上高中那会儿呀\N{\fnArial\fs16}You know, when I was in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我卯足干劲只为在游泳队谋得一席之位\N{\fnArial\fs16}I wanted more than anything to join the swim team...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别 求你别再说了\N{\fnArial\fs16}No! No! Please, not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈 你继续"想当年"的话\N{\fnArial\fs16}Mom, if you're going to reminisce,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕会逼我去求助社会服务署\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm afraid I'll be forced to call Social Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 Quinn 我换种方式说\N{\fnArial\fs16}All right, Quinn. Let me try to put it another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在生活中不管你决定要做什么 良好的教育都...\N{\fnArial\fs16}No matter what you decide to do in life, a solid education...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过这话啦 就是我被抓到逃...\N{\fnArial\fs16}You gave this talk when I got caught cutting my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是我忘了数学课在哪上的那次\N{\fnArial\fs16}when I forgot where my math class was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen 让我来\N{\fnArial\fs16}Helen, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你有没有听过蚂蚁和蚱蜢的故事?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Honey, did you ever here the tale of the ant and the grasshopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真恶心 虫耶?!\N{\fnArial\fs16}Ewwww! Bugs?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,试着这样想 Quinn...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Try imagining it this way, Quinn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会留级\N{\fnArial\fs16}You could be left back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,并变成朗岱尔高中最大龄的新生\N{\fnArial\fs16}and be the oldest freshman at Lawndale High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜咋地? 我要去学习了 拜\N{\fnArial\fs16}You know what? I gotta get to work. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是我的乖女\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's my girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧见了吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You see how it's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你在屋里吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Daria, are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不在 我在塔希提岛放松几天呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, I'm taking it easy in Tahiti for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等会哟 我要续一杯椰子得其利鸡尾酒呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hang on, I'm just ordering another tray of coconut daiquiris.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想能不能...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Um, I was wondering if...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不能\N{\fnArial\fs16}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,人家的作文需要一点帮助啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}I just need a little help with my essay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 你能不能帮我写嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Like, could you write it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我又要本着什么动机?\N{\fnArial\fs16}And what's my motivation again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托啦 Daria 我们是姐妹耶 我们得互相扶持\N{\fnArial\fs16}Come on, Daria, we're sisters! We gotta stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是公共场合除外吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Unless we're in public, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可你这么聪明 那作文又这么重要\N{\fnArial\fs16}But you're so smart, and this essay's so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我啦 我能写就写啦 可我有个约会\N{\fnArial\fs16}Believe me, I would do it myself, but I have a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 那可不一般\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, that's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,报酬怎么算?\N{\fnArial\fs16}When does the subject of compensation come up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,十块?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,二十\N{\fnArial\fs16}Twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,十五块\N{\fnArial\fs16}Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,成交\N{\fnArial\fs16}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢啦 Daria 这对我俩都有好处\N{\fnArial\fs16}Thanks, Daria. This is going to work out for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我能搞定我的作文\N{\fnArial\fs16}I mean, I get my essay written,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你至少也能给周五的夜晚找点寄托\N{\fnArial\fs16}and for once you'll have something to do on a Friday night
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不会像傻瓜似的无所事事 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}instead of sitting around like a loser, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 莎士比亚 你特么自个儿做吧你\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's it, Shakespeare. Do your own damn homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Quinn的家吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Um, is this Quinn's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是有一个叫Quinn的人住在这\N{\fnArial\fs16}Someone by that name does live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\fnArial\fs16}Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她在楼上做作业呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}She's upstairs doing schoolwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我就该对我拿到的地址留个心眼儿\N{\fnArial\fs16}I gotta pay more attention when I get these addresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Corey 我是下来告诉你我今晚不能约会啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Corey, I just came down to say I can't see you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要写作文\N{\fnArial\fs16}I have to write an essay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好借口 来嘛 我都为今晚制定好特殊计划啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Good one! Come on, I've got a special evening planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 趁汽车影院还没排长队前出发\N{\fnArial\fs16}Let's go! Before there's a line at the drive-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不 说真的 Corey 我得做作业 你得离开 对不起啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, really, Corey, I have work to do and you have to leave. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 他们到底怎么你了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn, what have they done to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你梳妆打扮了两小时\N{\fnArial\fs16}Did you just spend two hours dressing up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了在门口用一分钟放人家鸽子?\N{\fnArial\fs16}to go the door for one minute and dump your date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 如果你在最靓丽的时候拒绝一个男生\N{\fnArial\fs16}Daria, if you look your best when you blow a guy off,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就会觉得你是真的有在意\N{\fnArial\fs16}it makes them feel like you care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这建议应该会很有用\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, that advice should prove very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候你肤浅得如此透彻 几近深奥\N{\fnArial\fs16}Sometimes your shallowness is so thorough, it's almost like depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 算了 20就20吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Thanks. All right, twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fnArial\fs16}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好咯 希望你能意识到你在让我自力更生写作文\N{\fnArial\fs16}Fine! I hope you realize you're making me do my own homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这想法还真吓人\N{\fnArial\fs16}That is a scary thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我给大家带来了一个特别的惊喜哟\N{\fnArial\fs16}I have a special surprise everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,继上周的写作课后我们中有位同学大有进步\N{\fnArial\fs16}One of our students has so improved since last week's essay,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和大家分享一下她的作文\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm going to share her work with the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我真很喜欢你的紧身裤\N{\fnArial\fs16}I really like your leggings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不过我现在不知道要搭什么鞋子 绑带的么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, but now I have a shoe thing. Strappies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,穿有防水台的果冻鞋\N{\fnArial\fs16}Platform jellies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你真聪明\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn, you're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有对重要之事才会如此聪明\N{\fnArial\fs16}Only about important stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我没拿到作文\N{\fnArial\fs16}Um, I didn't get my paper back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你的确没拿到 Quinn 因为我要大声朗读它\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's right Quinn, because I'm going to read it aloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,《学术监禁》作者Quinn Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs16}"Academic Imprisonment," by Quinn Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"那接着来呀 用作业和试题禁锢我\N{\fnArial\fs16}"So go ahead! Lock me up with your homework and your tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,用阅读和思考夺走我的自由\N{\fnArial\fs16}Rob my freedom with your reading and your thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就我看来\N{\fnArial\fs16}As far as I'm concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,学校和监狱的唯一区别就只有衣橱罢了\N{\fnArial\fs16}the only difference between school and prison is the wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你想把我的衣服也夺走? 完毕"\N{\fnArial\fs16}Or do you want to take away my outfits, too? The End."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有人想做一下点评?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wow. Would anyone like to share their reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,请问我能转学么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}May I please change schools?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好哒 现在就能全面展示啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}There. Now it's on full display.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,像一扇成就之门\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quite the door of achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛 孩纸 你想鼓励你的妹妹吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Come on, kiddo. You want to encourage your sister, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在门上取得一席之位么 嗯\N{\fnArial\fs16}To get her own place, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 这是我的天才女儿\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hey! It's my daughter the genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们独一无二的尖子生\N{\fnArial\fs16}Our own academic achiever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都太为你骄傲了 对吧 Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs16}We're all so proud of you. Aren't we, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 如果你是指错愕的骄傲\N{\fnArial\fs16}Sure, if you mean proud as in "stunned."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妈咪 爸比 让你们欣慰是我想要求的最大奖励\N{\fnArial\fs16}Mom, Dad, making you happy is the greatest reward I can ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦 其他小孩取得好成绩时\N{\fnArial\fs16}Of course, when other kids get a good grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有时他们会得到一些小礼物呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}they sometimes get like a little present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 Quinn 我真觉得...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Now, Quinn, I really think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我来处理 你说得太对了 亲爱的\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'll handle this. You're absolutely right, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿到A 值得奖励 来 给你的\N{\fnArial\fs16}You get an A, you should be rewarded. Here ya go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢爸比\N{\fnArial\fs16}Thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 这不是双重标准吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wait. Isn't that a double standard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她拿个A 你就给她二十块钱\N{\fnArial\fs16}You just gave her a twenty for getting one A.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前拿的A全是义务劳动?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What about all the As I get for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可这是特殊情况\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, but this is a special occasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以Quinn就特别对待啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}so Quinn gets a special reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这关乎励志\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's a motivational thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可那不会让你各方面都一贯表现良好的...\N{\fnArial\fs16}But won't that demotivate your other daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个女儿消极么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}whose work is consistently good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 Jake 你要拿这怎么办?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yes, Jake, where are you going with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没处理完呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}I wasn't finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 一贯表现良好\N{\fnArial\fs16}Daria should have a consistent reward
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,值得持续性的奖励\N{\fnArial\fs16}for her consistently good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 在一次性特例中就得给...\N{\fnArial\fs16}And Quinn should have a special one-time reward
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一次性的特定奖励\N{\fnArial\fs16}for her one-time effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可长期保持表现良好\N{\fnArial\fs16}But what about a higher reward for maintaining
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,该得到更高的奖励吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}a standard of excellence over time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,算复合利息吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Perhaps with compound interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,行行行 都拿去\N{\fnArial\fs16}Here, just take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen 都和你说过我不擅长做教育工作啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Helen, I told you I was no good at this parenting crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Quinn 你红啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hey, Quinn, you're famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你们呀 我只是非常受欢迎而已啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, you guys. I'm just really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他是说你的作文上《朗岱尔内幕报》啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}He's talking about your essay in the Lawndale Lowdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,校报?!\N{\fnArial\fs16}The school paper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在《机灵想法》那栏\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's in the Smart Thoughts column.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我完了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,《学术监禁》作者Quinn Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs16}"Academic Imprisonment," by Quinn Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是很赞么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"阳光照不进这四面砖墙\N{\fnArial\fs16}"No light shines through these four brick walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为学校是我的牢房 老师是我的监守人"\N{\fnArial\fs16}For the school is my prison, and its teachers my imprisoners."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌你压根不知道有个词叫"监守人"吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'll bet you didn't even know that the word "imprisoners" existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不过我可迫不及待要学以致用啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, but now I can't wait to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底哪赞了?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Why exactly is this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为现在Quinn要尝尝\N{\fnArial\fs16}Because now Quinn's going to see firsthand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,做书呆子的滋味了\N{\fnArial\fs16}what is feels like to be a brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听听这话\N{\fnArial\fs16}Listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"像在那旋转笼子里跑着的仓鼠\N{\fnArial\fs16}"Like a hamster on one of those wheel things,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,学校让我们旋转不息\N{\fnArial\fs16}school runs us around and around
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,直至我们生出对饲料的渴望\N{\fnArial\fs16}until we yearn for the little food pellet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但等待我们的只有更多的作业"\N{\fnArial\fs16}But only more homework awaits."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你造吗 就好像她能读取我的心思呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}You know, it's like she read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,恰好在你头部严重受创后\N{\fnArial\fs16}Right after you suffered a severe blow of the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把那报纸收起来么? 到处都是\N{\fnArial\fs16}Could you put that away? They're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这干嘛? 你坐的那张桌有炸弹么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What are you doing here? Bomb scare at your table?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小声点 行吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Keep it down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,自从校报发行后 我就一直想保持低调\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm trying to keep a low profile since the paper came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你真走运 普利策委员会刚吃饱饭\N{\fnArial\fs16}Lucky for you, the Pulitzer committee already finished eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\an8}美国普利策奖 分有新闻奖和文学艺术奖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们吃了肉卷\N{\fnArial\fs16}They had the meatloaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定对别人怎么称呼你很激动吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}You must be very excited about what people are calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么称呼?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,智者Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs16}"Brains" Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 就因为一篇小作文?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Come on, because of one little essay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是下坡路 看呐 你的未来写照\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's a slippery slope. Behold, the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,上周 他们去参加橄榄球甄选\N{\fnArial\fs16}Last week, they were trying out for football,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,结果赢了一个辩论赛\N{\fnArial\fs16}then they won one debate tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我要怎么办? 我不能做书呆子\N{\fnArial\fs16}What am I gonna do? I can't be a brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友们会讨厌我的\N{\fnArial\fs16}My friends will hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 但只要你想想你会在棋艺社交到新朋友\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yes, but just think of all the new friends you'll make in Chess Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我该趁其他人还没读到校报\N{\fnArial\fs16}Maybe I can steal all the newspapers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就把它们全偷走\N{\fnArial\fs16}before anyone else reads them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 不对劲啊 智者\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hey, wait a minute, "Brains."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你这时段不应该是在吃饭吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You don't even have lunch this period, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是啦 我翘掉科学课来找你\N{\fnArial\fs16}Of course not! I cut Science to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我年级的人都在饭堂 我会和你坐一桌嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You think I'd sit with you while my grade is at lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还是在讨论"做书呆子绝壁错误"?\N{\fnArial\fs16}About that being mistaken for a brain thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不怎么担心\N{\fnArial\fs16}I wouldn't worry too much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底为什么要在自修室学习?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Why do you have to study during study hall, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn在辅导我的英语\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn's tutoring me in English
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就能继续待在球队了 这是O'Neill老师的指令\N{\fnArial\fs16}so I can stay on the football team. Mr. O'Neill set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevvy 我也能辅导你 我也讲英语呀\N{\fnArial\fs16}Kevvy, I could tutor you! I speak English too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 我想到一个主意了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Babe, I've got a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好想到了 你 你个卡萨布兰卡小毛头\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'll bet you do, you, you high school Casablanca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不 宝贝 我是为了我俩才这么做的\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, babe, I'm doing this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是要去观察聪明人的行为\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm going to, like, observe the way a brain acts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就能加以模仿并变酷啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}and then we could act that way and be cool, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevvy 你太聪明啦 你在我眼里早就是聪明人啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, Kevvy. You're so smart. You're already a brain in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢哟 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs16}Thanks, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只有Quinn才能把聪明变成时代的潮流\N{\fnArial\fs16}Only Quinn could turn being smart into a fad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,甭担心 今天流行聪明 明天穿个舌孔\N{\fnArial\fs16}Don't worry. Today it's brains, tomorrow pierced tongues,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,接着后天给脑子也打个洞\N{\fnArial\fs16}then the next day, pierced brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 反正这对她也没差\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, it's not like it's going to get her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以O'Neill老师就说我可以免听剩下的课\N{\fnArial\fs16}So then Mr. O'Neill said I could skip the rest of his class
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,早点吃午饭\N{\fnArial\fs16}and go to lunch early
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我领悟得太快了\N{\fnArial\fs16}because I was catching on so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你想见我?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You asked to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你知道我很崇拜你写的作文\N{\fnArial\fs16}Daria, you know I'm a big, big fan of your writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可最近 你写的东西有点儿 怎么说呢 平淡\N{\fnArial\fs16}But lately, it seems kinda of, I don't know, flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我期待你能写点更... 花哨的东西\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm looking for something a little more... jazzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\an8}jazzy也译爵士乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我来段架子鼓独奏?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You want me to put in a drum solo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是想知道你对于一对一辅导的看法\N{\fnArial\fs16}I was wondering how you'd feel about some one-on-one tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有点像迷你写作研讨会\N{\fnArial\fs16}Sort of a mini writing workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你见一个人\N{\fnArial\fs16}There's somebody I want you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她应该随时会...\N{\fnArial\fs16}She should be here any ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你想让我... 辅导谁吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hi, you wanted me to... ...help somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们认识呀?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Do you two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就该说 "我才不用学她的写作方式\N{\fnArial\fs16}I should have said, "I don't need tutoring to write like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,和蜡笔画似的"\N{\fnArial\fs16}Just some big crayons."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真是糟糕\N{\fnArial\fs16}Tough day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不会让这事影响我\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm not letting it get to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大家看呀 我在吃薯条的时候又写了另外一首诗\N{\fnArial\fs16}Look everyone! I wrote another poem while I was eating my fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,到我来朗读了\N{\fnArial\fs16}My turn to read!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"油乎乎的薯条 它不会撒谎\N{\fnArial\fs16}"The greasy fry, it cannot lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真相就写在你的大腿上"\N{\fnArial\fs16}Its truth is written on your thighs."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 Quinn 真是超赞的耶\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wow. Quinn. That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,文风优美\N{\fnArial\fs16}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天才\N{\fnArial\fs16}Genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,且慢 我觉得我要文思泉涌了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hold it. I think I feel a poem coming on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 虚惊一场\N{\fnArial\fs16}Sorry, false alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我可能会从事写作这行\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, I might do writing for a career.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这不算什么真正的工作\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's not like real work or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 我是说 打字有什么难的嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Really. I mean, how hard it is to type stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多机会呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}And there are lots of opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你造他们会在贺卡里加入诗歌吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Like, did you know they pay money
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你造他们会在贺卡里加入诗歌吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}for those poems inside greeting cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,噢不 我一直都无偿替他们写诗啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh no! I've been giving my poems away for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我一个忙么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Do me a favor, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,关上柜门\N{\fnArial\fs16}Close my locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哑剧大师爬进来死在这了?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Did a mime crawl in here and die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我在搭配衣服啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm putting together an outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,供你参考一下 人们就是这么注重着装\N{\fnArial\fs16}For your information, this is how deep people dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 十分注重做作的人\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, deeply affected people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\an8}西方存在主义哲学流派\N以人为中心 尊重人的个性和自由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 对了 你知道存在主义是什么意思吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Thank you. By the way, do you know what existential means?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因为今天有人说我的作文很存在主义\N{\fnArial\fs16}Because today someone told me my writing was existential,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想我要调整一下 用衣服来调整\N{\fnArial\fs16}so I thought I should coordinate, you know, with wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对 那就是加缪会做的事\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, that's what Camus would have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\an8}存在主义文学领军人物 荒诞哲学的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,根据你的情况 存在主义是指\N{\fnArial\fs16}For your purposes, existential means
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"穿戴着街市里买来的配件的伪知识分子"\N{\fnArial\fs16}"pseudo-intellectual poser with accessories from the street fair."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 要是你想让我辅导你的作文 我会帮你的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Listen, I'm still available if you want help with your writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这黑色和项链配不配?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Does this black match?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,和我的心情配\N{\fnArial\fs16}Matches my mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,叛变的外科医生会趁你睡着移植你的大脑吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Can renegade surgeons transplant your brain while you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来为您播出《呕心小世界: 可怕的真相》\N{\fnArial\fs16}The frightening truth, next on Sick, Sad World.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是有心事 Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Is something bothering you, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fnArial\fs16}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 和老爸谈谈心也未尝不可\N{\fnArial\fs16}You know, it's all right to have a heart to heart with Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是做过不少家长工作的嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}I've been known to do a little parenting in my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想什么? 我来解决\N{\fnArial\fs16}What's on your mind? I'm up on the issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,毒品 同辈压力... 还是帮派出事了?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Drugs, peer pressure... or is it a problem with your gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,说是我个人问题比较恰当\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's more of a personal issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什么... 保健问题吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's not... hygiene or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 就假设你有一个你不怎么喜欢的身份\N{\fnArial\fs16}Dad, let's say you have an identity that you didn't even like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好哇 比如有天醒来发现自己人到中年\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, sure! Like, one day you wake up middle aged
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恨得很想逃离\N{\fnArial\fs16}and resenting the hell out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Um, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是尽管你不喜欢这种身份\N{\fnArial\fs16}But even though you don't like this identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有人突然就抢了你的风头\N{\fnArial\fs16}somebody suddenly comes along and steals it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你对此很沮丧 你本来就得到那种身份了\N{\fnArial\fs16}And you're upset. You earned that resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那已是你的权利了嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}it's your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 更像是 你的确不想要这种身份\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, it's more like, you didn't want this identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可有人把它抢走的话 你就什么都没有了\N{\fnArial\fs16}but if they take it away, you've got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们抢走你的身份了吗 Daria? 那你就一走了之\N{\fnArial\fs16}They took your identity, Daria? Then you walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,改头换姓 搬去别的州 弄张身份证\N{\fnArial\fs16}You change your name, move to another state, get some ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,重新开始永远都不迟 Daria 永远都不迟\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's not too late to start over, Daria, it's not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你还年轻\N{\fnArial\fs16}You're still a young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用背负错误过活\N{\fnArial\fs16}You don't have to live with your mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要适时离开\N{\fnArial\fs16}Get out while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会要摇我肩膀吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Um, you're not going to shake me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我要说的是\N{\fnArial\fs16}What I meant was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持下去 那一切都会好起来的\N{\fnArial\fs16}you hang in there and everything's going to work out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 和你聊完 我感觉好多了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Dad, talking to you has made me feel better about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是应该的 孩纸\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's what I'm here for, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,伴唱人员 哈\N{\fnArial\fs16}Backup singer. Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚发现诗歌用不着押韵耶\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, I just found out poems don't even have to rhyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,多简单呀?\N{\fnArial\fs16}How easy is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,出事了 Quinn 我们得谈一谈\N{\fnArial\fs16}There's a problem, Quinn. We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好像其他女生都在效仿你的怪异行径\N{\fnArial\fs16}It seems that other girls are following your weirdo example
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃时尚行头 穿得一身黑\N{\fnArial\fs16}and abandoning their fashion statements to wear all black.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一身黑也是时尚行头\N{\fnArial\fs16}Dressing in black is a fashion statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它有深度 有意义 还显瘦\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's deep, it's meaningful, and it's slenderizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,杂志才不是这样说的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Not according to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道深紫色才是当前流行的暗色\N{\fnArial\fs16}Everyone knows that eggplant is the current neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 我也阻止不了自己在这有影响力呀\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, I can't help it if I have influence around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,人们尊敬我的智慧\N{\fnArial\fs16}People admire me for my brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不是时尚俱乐部的教条\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's not how the Fashion Club works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在下令你正式放假 一直放到...\N{\fnArial\fs16}You're officially ordered to take a fashion sabbatical
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞清楚事情的轻重为止\N{\fnArial\fs16}until you get your priorities straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我很担心Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm concerned about Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得找她亲近的人\N{\fnArial\fs16}We need someone close to her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,来让她意识到自己行为不当\N{\fnArial\fs16}to make her see the error of her ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可要找谁?\N{\fnArial\fs16}But who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个计划 我们去和她认识的那女生聊聊\N{\fnArial\fs16}I had a plan. We'll talk to that girl she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你真聪明 Sandi\N{\fnArial\fs16}You're so smart, Sandi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你们还会发现我对此从不炫耀\N{\fnArial\fs16}And you'll notice I don't make, like, a big thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可那个女生很诡异\N{\fnArial\fs16}But that girl is so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她吓坏我了\N{\fnArial\fs16}She freaks me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这就为什么我能当时尚俱乐部的主席了\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's why I'm president of the Fashion Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我来搞定她\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'll handle her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得那是要干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What do you think that was about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们永远都猜不透\N{\fnArial\fs16}I supposed we'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane 看仔细点\N{\fnArial\fs16}Jane, look carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我有长出另外一个头么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Have I grown another head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 就两个\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, just the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,再会\N{\fnArial\fs16}See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么了?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没怎么\N{\fnArial\fs16}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有要脑力帮忙解决的事?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Anything a little brain power could fix?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜她自己能搞定\N{\fnArial\fs16}I think she's had about her fill of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,能问你个问题吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}I guess. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得我是书呆子吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You don't think I'm a brain, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没这样觉得过\N{\fnArial\fs16}The thought never crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有\N{\fnArial\fs16}Mine, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 我很享受这样能打击到Daria\N{\fnArial\fs16}I mean, I really like the way this getting to Daria,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可我开始感到我是冒牌货了\N{\fnArial\fs16}but I'm starting to feel like a phoney.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你开始感觉自己是冒牌货?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You're starting to feel like a phoney?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不就写了篇傻不拉几的作文嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}So I wrote a stupid essay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大家干嘛要这么在意?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What's everyone making such a big deal about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 人们对什么事都不抱期待的话\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, you know, condition people to expect nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那屁大点事都能让他们嗨起来\N{\fnArial\fs16}and the least little something gets them all excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,问巴普洛夫去\N{\fnArial\fs16}Ask Pavlov.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\an8}苏联生理学家和实验心理学家 提出"条件反射论"\N高级神经活动生理学的奠基人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,管理员?\N{\fnArial\fs16}The custodian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,随便了 话不投机半句多\N{\fnArial\fs16}Never mind. Return to your world, and I'll return to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 什么事在蚕食你的灵魂嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}By the way, anything eating away at your soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她的作文很烂\N{\fnArial\fs16}Her writing's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,难道人们连好和坏都分辨不清了么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Don't people know the difference between good and bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她漂亮 长得好看的人适用于不同的标准\N{\fnArial\fs16}She's cute. There's different standards for cute people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的是没有标准吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}You mean, no standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fnArial\fs16}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是曾经有过不以貌取人的岁月么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Isn't there ever a time when how you look
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是曾经有过不以貌取人的岁月么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}doesn't affect how you're judged?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,除非是在你把眼睛作为捐献器官的岁月\N{\fnArial\fs16}When you donate an organ, unless it's your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 这没什么大不了的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Listen, it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,重点在于 如果她是书呆子 那我是什么啊?\N{\fnArial\fs16}The thing is, if she's a brain, what do I get to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是书呆子\N{\fnArial\fs16}You're still a brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是 可她是有一头秀发的书呆子\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, but she's a brain with bouncy hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我比不过\N{\fnArial\fs16}I can't compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 那你就是... 超级书呆子\N{\fnArial\fs16}Okay, then you get to be... a super-brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,比之前的更形影单只\N{\fnArial\fs16}An even bigger outcast than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我才胜任不了超级书呆子呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}I don't think I can survive being a super-brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,到时她自然会停止了 不过要怎么才停?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Then she's got to be stopped. But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我造了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, I know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是没让自己这么做... 直到现在\N{\fnArial\fs16}I just haven't been able to bring myself to do it... until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不 搞错了 我们以为...\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, um, it's a mistake. We thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你眯眼眯够的话\N{\fnArial\fs16}If you squinted hard enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可能我会变成另外一款Morgendorffer?\N{\fnArial\fs16}maybe I'd look like a different Morgendorffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 你们真想要Quinn回归本性?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Look, do you really want Quinn back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是\N{\fnArial\fs16}A thousand times yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,让她回来\N{\fnArial\fs16}Bring her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你得让她回来\N{\fnArial\fs16}You gotta bring her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,服从我的命令 我就交货\N{\fnArial\fs16}Do exactly what I say, and I'll deliver the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 能帮我拿瓶苏打么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hi! Could you get me a soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计 咋滴捏?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hey, dudes! Whazzup?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你约的人到啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn! Your dates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我们是来约Daria的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Actually, we're here to ask Daria out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你另外一个女儿啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}You know, your other daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 Quinn怎么样啦?\N{\fnArial\fs16}By the way, how's Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 Jamie\N{\fnArial\fs16}Shut up, Jamie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hi, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hi, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 我要下去赴约了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, I'm off for my dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,1... 2...\N{\fnArial\fs16}One... two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你赢了 行了吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Ugh! Wait! You win, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我是没写作文\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, I didn't even write the essay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我在垃圾桶找到一篇就交上去了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I found it in the garbage and handed it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,整件事就像失控的火车\N{\fnArial\fs16}The whole thing was, like, a runaway train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 不过还是解释不通黑衣黑裤的事\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, that still doesn't explain black clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我想这就算了\N{\fnArial\fs16}but I guess I can let it slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 我受够做知识分子了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Don't worry, I'm through being an intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我太能适应环境\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm too well-adjusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,找脑子的茬 可是很危险的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Messing with the mind can be so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,说说看\N{\fnArial\fs16}Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜一切都恢复正常了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I guess things are back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,时尚: 好 思考: 烂\N{\fnArial\fs16}Fashion: good. Thinking: bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们赢喽\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah. We win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我屹立于世界之巅\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm on top of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\fn迷你简汉真广标\fsp1\c&HF6FCF9&\pos(295,130)}欢迎微博关注\N\N{\fs25}@漫迪字幕组
